{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|Jol|3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jol","chapter":3,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v10","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jol:3:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jol","bookOrder":28,"chapter":3,"verse":1,"text":"Yes, in those days and at that time,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jol:3:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jol","bookOrder":28,"chapter":3,"verse":2,"text":"I will gather all the nations","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jol:3:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jol","bookOrder":28,"chapter":3,"verse":3,"text":"They cast lots for my people;","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jol:3:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jol","bookOrder":28,"chapter":3,"verse":4,"text":"And also: Tyre, Sidon, and all the territories of Philistia —what are you to me? Are you paying me back or trying to get even with me? I will quickly bring retribution on your heads.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jol:3:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jol","bookOrder":28,"chapter":3,"verse":5,"text":"For you took my silver and gold and carried my finest treasures to your temples.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jol:3:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jol","bookOrder":28,"chapter":3,"verse":6,"text":"You sold the people of Judah and Jerusalem to the Greeks to remove them far from their own territory.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jol:3:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jol","bookOrder":28,"chapter":3,"verse":7,"text":"Look, I am about to rouse them up from the place where you sold them; I will bring retribution on your heads.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jol:3:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jol","bookOrder":28,"chapter":3,"verse":8,"text":"I will sell your sons and daughters to the people of Judah, and they will sell them to the Sabeans, to a distant nation, for the Lord has spoken.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jol:3:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jol","bookOrder":28,"chapter":3,"verse":9,"text":"Proclaim this among the nations:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jol:3:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jol","bookOrder":28,"chapter":3,"verse":10,"text":"Beat your plows into swords","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jol:3:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jol","bookOrder":28,"chapter":3,"verse":11,"text":"Come quickly, all you surrounding nations;","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jol:3:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jol","bookOrder":28,"chapter":3,"verse":12,"text":"Let the nations be roused","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jol:3:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jol","bookOrder":28,"chapter":3,"verse":13,"text":"Swing the sickle","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jol:3:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jol","bookOrder":28,"chapter":3,"verse":14,"text":"Multitudes, multitudes","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jol:3:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jol","bookOrder":28,"chapter":3,"verse":15,"text":"The sun and moon will grow dark,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jol:3:16","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jol","bookOrder":28,"chapter":3,"verse":16,"text":"The Lord will roar from Zion","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jol:3:17","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jol","bookOrder"